ISLAMABAD, Dec 19 (APP):Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib said on Sunday that after forty one years, Pakistan was hosting a meeting of OIC Council of Foreign Ministers in view of the humanitarian crisis in Afghanistan.
The presence of high level delegations from many countries in Pakistan was a manifestation of its excellent and dynamic foreign policy.
